===Etymology===
The origin is {{unk|hy|title=unknown}}. Confined to Eastern dialects, with the earliest attestation in the 17th century.<ref>{{R:xcl:Liak|vol=I|page=71}}</ref> Ačaṙyan remarks that derivation from {{noncog|xcl|-ագոյն}} (of Iranian origin) is impossible, because no {{m|hy||գ}} → {{m|hy||վ}} sound change is known in the dialects. But perhaps that change occurred within an {{bor|hy|ira}} language, where such a change is known, and thence was borrowed into Armenian.

Compare also {{cog|ckb|-ئەوِن}}, forming adjectives from nouns.

